{"tid":1183392,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【順應潮流】蘋果公司申請專利設計 屏幕可不同方向屈摺","createTime":"2019-06-03T01:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T11:20:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"398a3c2c48344647fcc4d7776192fcc92ee265e6","tid":1183392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"近年摺機潮流回歸，蘋果也有可能跟隨潮流，蘋果公司近期向美國提交專利圖，申請「雙摺」屏幕設計，外界估計蘋果或者準備推出自己開發的摺機。<br />\n網媒《Apple Patently》指，蘋果在美國提交的專利圖中，可見摺機的屏幕可以「向後摺」成一個「S」型，或是向內摺變成一個「G」型（右圖），但到底蘋果會否推出摺機，則仍屬未知之數。有關技術如果成真，意味手機也可以在展開時當成平板電腦使用。<br />\n專利圖指手機會有一個旋轉鉸鏈，讓屏幕折疊在一起，同時可以由180度變為90度，新設計估計不只用於iPhone，有可能用於iPad、MacBook、甚至Apple Watch。由於專利圖提供的新機資料不多，網媒《foldable.news》請來荷蘭產品設計師吉爾辛（Roy Gilsing）畫出蘋果iPhone摺機概念圖（左圖）。<br />\n近年其他大廠如華為及三星相繼推出摺機裝置，其中三星的Galaxy Fold被視為市場先導者，但今年推出後反應太差，外媒試用一兩日後紛紛發現新機的屏幕出現問題，多人稱自己的新機用了一兩天就壞掉。華為的Mate X在今年展出時被認為比三星的摺機更好用，但由於Google加入封殺華為，手機銷情慘淡。另一間公開了摺機設計的公司是Oppo，年初公開了摺機的測試機，與華為Mate X一樣採用外翻式設計，僅有一個屏幕，但未有打算量產。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190602/large/1559452862_9434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190602%2Flarge%2F1559452862_9434.jpg&h=6427882d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由其他公司設計的概念圖（左）；蘋果提交的專利圖（右）(互聯網)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190602/large/1559454824_4c70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190602%2Flarge%2F1559454824_4c70.jpg&h=c7053ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荷蘭產品設計師吉爾辛畫出蘋果iPhone摺機概念圖。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190602/59667544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59667544&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=009d89cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F59667544&h=74854474\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190602/59667544</a>"},{"pid":"71283f6c8f332c1e865d7e95812728022f02196a","tid":1183392,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:15:40.000Z","msg":"艾fan又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c481d7b461d0a25ca4da00246535921ef00e78c","tid":1183392,"uid":22553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:15:59.000Z","msg":"apple有幾多樣野申請完專利又唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb752900b9d09a4fe31cf1f46c1d054588cb38d4","tid":1183392,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c481d7b461d0a25ca4da00246535921ef00e78c","tid":1183392,"uid":22553,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:15:59.000Z","msg":"apple有幾多樣野申請完專利又唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:17:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://samsung-updates.com/samsung-receives-a-patent-for-padfone-like-phone-to-tablet-dock-technology/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsamsung-updates.com%2Fsamsung-receives-a-patent-for-padfone-like-phone-to-tablet-dock-technology%2F&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=7e11d787\" target=\"_blank\">http://samsung-updates.com/samsung-receives-a-patent-for-padfone-like-phone-to-tablet-dock-technology/</a>"},{"pid":"45e87efc5b26c13e642eaeeb8fc119a4b1e83d93","tid":1183392,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"做到先講 airpower都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b967445e667bf2c0587d6bf063b9448f6a0419","tid":1183392,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T01:19:40.000Z","msg":"個荷蘭設計師好L懶"},{"pid":"b19e813387b09d9cdc416563f9c7e4636601fe24","tid":1183392,"uid":89514,